atd.pillage
Class StatsCollectorImpl

java.lang.Object
  atd.pillage.StatsCollectorImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
StatsCollector
public class StatsCollectorImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements StatsCollector

Attaches to a StatsContainer and reports on all the counters, metrics, gauges, and labels. Each report resets state, so counters are reported as deltas, and metrics distributions are only tracked since the last report.
